snippet.title: Fun(c)tional Programming Group
snippet.description:
This is the channel for programmers of all levels to learn about functional programming (FP).
We welcome all functional languages including (but not limited to) Scala, Erlang, Haskell, Clojure, F#.
We are also interested in technologies associated with FP like reactive programming, message passing architectures, the actor model, etc.

The channel is focused on learning functional principles using mathematics, understanding scenarios where it is better to use FP, discovering new languages and technologies and exploring best practices in FP.

web: https://www.meetup.com/fun-c-group/
twitter: @fun_c_

Hosted by Expedia Group, Inc.
"We are the World’s Travel Platform. Bringing the world within reach"
Expedia Group is hiring (see https://lifeatexpedia.com)
If you want to join us please reach one of the hosts.
